&lt;p&gt;Dive into the heart of the city at AVANI Deira. Breathe in the scent of spices as you walk through hidden passages. Haggle over gold in world-famous souks. Take a short hop to the beach to chill on the sands with a stunning city backdrop. Conveniently located for business travellers just a short drive from Dubai International Airport. Mix business and pleasure in the culturally rich district of Dubai.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Stay for two or more nights to get extra perks and double the fun with late check out, daily breakfast, a room upgrade, and more!&lt;br /&gt;
･ 20% off Rooms&lt;br /&gt;
･ Inclusive of daily breakfast&lt;br /&gt;
･ Complimentary upgrade to the next room category (subject to availability on arrival)&lt;br /&gt;
･ Complimentary late check-out (subject to availability on departure)&lt;br /&gt;
･ WiFi internet access&lt;br /&gt;
Please quote your exclusive promotion code DINERS, and show your valid Diners Club International card at check-in to qualify for special rate or Best Flexible Rate at time of check-in will be applied. Additional benefits offered through the promotion are not applicable if making payment with a different card. Please visit avanihotels.com/dinersoffer for the complete terms and conditions.&lt;/p&gt;

